00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:35,560
(We should turn this recruiting process)

284
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:37,800
(into a process of mobilizing
young intellectuals and school students)

285
00:14:38,040 --> 00:14:40,440
(to learn knowledge for the revolution)

286
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:43,160
(more actively and consciously,)

287
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:46,280
(and to take the right path.)

288
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:56,920
Come on, let's go.

289
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,160
Ye Fang, are you okay?

290
00:15:00,160 --> 00:15:01,280
I'm fine, your bag!

291
00:15:02,560 --> 00:15:03,720
My admission ticket is in it.

292
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:06,040
Hongjun!

293
00:15:17,400 --> 00:15:19,040
Fang, aren't you taking the exam today?

294
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:20,000
- Chunsheng.
- What's going on?

295
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:22,560
Hongjun's admission ticket
and bag were taken.

296
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:23,400
Wait.

297
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:24,360
I'm going to find Hongjun.

298
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:25,160
Here, take my bike.

299
00:15:25,160 --> 00:15:25,720
Wait for us at the examination place.

300
00:15:25,800 --> 00:15:27,400
Don't worry, I won't let Hongjun miss it.

301
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:28,040
OK.

302
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:30,720
Chunsheng, be careful.

303
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:33,280
Stop!

304
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:39,960
Heizi?

305
00:15:41,040 --> 00:15:41,840
Li Shangyou?

306
00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:49,680
Wanna run?

307
00:15:55,940 --> 00:15:57,620
(Examination Admission Ticket)

308
00:15:58,640 --> 00:15:59,480
Chen Hongjun,

309
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:01,800
about my eye,

310
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:03,920
we have an account

311
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:06,080
to settle.

312
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,040
Heizi,

313
00:16:07,920 --> 00:16:09,000
if you do this,

314
00:16:09,400 --> 00:16:11,120
Chunsheng will make you pay.

315
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:13,560
Xiao Chunsheng?

316
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:15,880
He will make me pay?

317
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:17,400
You know what,

318
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:19,440
I'll go to him
right after I'm done with you.

319
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:22,760
No, please!

320
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:25,280
I'm begging you.

321
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:26,960
Give me back the admission ticket first.

322
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:28,360
After I finish the exam,

323
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:29,920
the three of us

324
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:31,600
will discuss this matter

325
00:16:31,920 --> 00:16:33,000
and come up with a solution.

326
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:35,080
I guarantee you will be satisfied, OK?

327
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:37,200
Please!

328
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:39,480
How about this?

329
00:16:39,760 --> 00:16:40,840
Just name a condition now,

330
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:43,080
and I'll meet it no matter what.

331
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:45,000
So many people are here today,

332
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:46,080
and they can bear witness for us.

333
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:48,360
I, Chen Hongjun,
will never break my promise.

334
00:16:52,580 --> 00:16:54,860
(Beijing Lixin Middle School)

335
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:00,720
I've been preparing

336
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,360
for this exam for two years.

337
00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:04,560
Please do me a favor and let me go.

338
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:05,560
Please!

339
00:17:10,760 --> 00:17:11,560
Two years?

340
00:17:12,630 --> 00:17:13,350
Two years.

341
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:17,920
Give it another two years.

342
00:17:18,390 --> 00:17:18,960
No, don't!

343
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:19,560
Stop it!

344
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,630
Chunsheng.

345
00:17:26,870 --> 00:17:27,480
Chunsheng.

346
00:17:30,120 --> 00:17:32,760
Xiao Chunsheng, why are you everywhere?

347
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:34,520
I warn you,

348
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:36,680
stay out of this. It's not your turn yet!

349
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:39,520
Heizi, what do you want?

350
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:40,920
Just say it.

351
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,280
What do I want?

352
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:46,520
I don't know if I can

353
00:17:46,520 --> 00:17:47,560
have this eye back.

354
00:17:48,280 --> 00:17:51,200
I'll take one of his eyes,

355
00:17:51,520 --> 00:17:52,320
or

356
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:53,760
I'll stab you with a sharpened steel tube

357
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:55,080
as Tian said,

358
00:17:55,120 --> 00:17:56,400
and then we will be even.

359
00:18:01,980 --> 00:18:04,740
(Welcome to the Participants
of the 1977 College Entrance Examination)

360
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:06,120
Thank you.

361
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:07,560
Thank you.

362
00:18:07,960 --> 00:18:08,520
Your admission ticket, please.

363
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:09,120
Good luck.

364
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:09,920
Let me see.

365
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,000
OK, good luck.

366
00:18:11,360 --> 00:18:12,000
Thanks.

367
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:15,360
Go for it.

368
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:16,040
Okay, thank you.

369
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:18,640
See?

370
00:18:18,840 --> 00:18:19,920
This is your best friend.

371
00:18:20,040 --> 00:18:21,080
You think he'll save you?

372
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:25,240
Do it.

373
00:18:25,760 --> 00:18:26,400
Chunsheng.

374
00:18:26,800 --> 00:18:27,520
No, Chunsheng.

375
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:28,720
Chunsheng.

376
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:30,600
Chunsheng.

377
00:18:37,080 --> 00:18:37,840
You...

378
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:51,400
Heizi,

379
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:55,400
it must be Xiaohui who told him.

380
00:19:00,560 --> 00:19:01,280
Chunsheng!

381
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:02,680
Chunsheng.

382
00:19:17,560 --> 00:19:19,720
Chunsheng. Chunsheng. Chunsheng.

383
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:29,080
Chunsheng.

384
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:40,160
Xiao Chunsheng, you are a real man.

385
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,440
- This matter is over.
- Chunsheng.

386
00:19:44,320 --> 00:19:45,880
Go! You are running late.

387
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,440
You will always be my big brother.

388
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:49,400
No time for that.

389
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:50,680
Fang is waiting for you.

390
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:51,960
Go now.

391
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:02,240
(Invigilator)
Girl, the bell is ringing for the last time.

392
00:20:02,520 --> 00:20:03,120
There's no time.

393
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:04,280
Get in or you'll be late.

394
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:09,240
Come on.

395
00:20:14,320 --> 00:20:14,760
Chunsheng.

396
00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:16,400
I'm fine. Come on!

397
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:19,960
Hongjun, what took you so long?

398
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:21,640
Don't dawdle, just go in.

399
00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:22,000
Come on.

400
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:22,640
Wait a minute.

401
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:23,360
Your admission ticket.

402
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:24,200
Admission ticket.

403
00:20:25,620 --> 00:20:26,980
(Examination Admission Ticket
Chen Hongjun)

404
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:28,320
OK. Get in now.

405
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:29,400
Come on.

406
00:20:29,760 --> 00:20:30,640
Good luck!

407
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:32,120
Get in now.

408
00:20:32,120 --> 00:20:32,560
Come on.

409
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:05,880
You're awake.

410
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:10,840
Xiao... Xiaomei?

411
00:21:13,080 --> 00:21:14,160
Why are you here?

412
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:18,000
I'm the nurse on duty
at the exam place near here.

413
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:19,960
Someone found you on the ground

414
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,160
and sent you here.

415
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:28,960
You are really treating me now.

416
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:33,520
Fortunately, the wound is not deep.

417
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:34,680
The bleeding has been stopped.

418
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:36,640
It was close.

419
00:21:37,080 --> 00:21:38,520
Don't let this happen again.

420
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:41,080
I also don't want this to happen again.

421
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:45,280
Now I just want both of them

422
00:21:45,600 --> 00:21:46,760
to be admitted to a good university.

423
00:21:48,280 --> 00:21:50,880
That way, my wound would not be in vain.

424
00:21:52,480 --> 00:21:53,040
By the way,

425
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:55,680
Ye Fang and Hongjun

426
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:58,120
came to visit you after the morning exam,

427
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,280
but you were not awake,

428
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:01,440
so they went back for the afternoon exam.

429
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:04,640
Are you hungry?

430
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:08,400
Here, eat something.

431
00:22:10,040 --> 00:22:12,760
Well, I'm a little hungry indeed.

432
00:22:20,080 --> 00:22:20,960
Thank you, Xiaomei.

433
00:22:58,020 --> 00:23:00,340
(See you in the boiler room at 3:00 p.m.)

434
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:26,560
I'm sorry for what you experienced.

435
00:23:27,840 --> 00:23:29,360
You did that to me.

436
00:23:31,400 --> 00:23:32,320
Yes, I know.

437
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:34,880
But it doesn't mean I don't feel sorry.

438
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:38,320
You are bold.

439
00:23:40,120 --> 00:23:41,040
I'm not that bold.

440
00:23:41,600 --> 00:23:42,760
It took me half a day

441
00:23:42,760 --> 00:23:44,000
to nerve myself.

442
00:23:44,720 --> 00:23:45,960
My heart is still racing.

443
00:23:47,320 --> 00:23:48,160
Feel it if you don't believe me.

444
00:23:48,600 --> 00:23:49,360
Let go of my hand!

445
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:56,480
You hate me,

446
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:57,840
right?

447
00:23:58,720 --> 00:23:59,880
What do you think?

448
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:01,200
That's good.

449
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:04,480
That means you care about me.

450
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:09,480
Listen,

451
00:24:09,760 --> 00:24:11,280
Heizi is simple.

452
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:12,880
He really treats you like a brother.

453
00:24:14,760 --> 00:24:15,840
I can't believe

454
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,920
you are still thinking about him.

455
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,440
He is just a simpleton

456
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:23,240
who is not good enough for you.

457
00:24:25,560 --> 00:24:26,160
See?

458
00:24:26,240 --> 00:24:28,320
What did you get for being loyal to him?

459
00:24:31,120 --> 00:24:31,680
I know

460
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:36,320
they are very kind,

461
00:24:39,080 --> 00:24:40,080
but they are also so stupid

462
00:24:40,320 --> 00:24:41,640
that they prefer to believe lies.

463
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:45,080
We are smart people.

464
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:47,040
We'll just tell them

465
00:24:47,040 --> 00:24:48,320
what they like to hear.

466
00:24:48,320 --> 00:24:51,160
They will be happy this way,
isn't it good?

467
00:24:52,560 --> 00:24:54,120
You should learn your lesson.

468
00:24:58,080 --> 00:24:58,800
OK.

469
00:24:59,800 --> 00:25:00,720
Enough of this.

470
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:02,960
Let me tell you something serious.

471
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:08,360
Xiaohui,

472
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:11,840
since the first time I saw you,

473
00:25:12,080 --> 00:25:13,760
I've never stopped thinking about you.

474
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:17,120
And I miss you crazily every day.

475
00:25:19,520 --> 00:25:20,720
I want to be with you.

476
00:25:24,040 --> 00:25:24,960
Li Shangyou,

477
00:25:25,800 --> 00:25:27,040
you are too confident.

478
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,720
Sooner or later
you will die because of this.

479
00:25:32,720 --> 00:25:33,640
It doesn't matter.

480
00:25:35,120 --> 00:25:36,040
I'm willing

481
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:38,800
to die for you.

482
00:25:40,360 --> 00:25:41,000
OK.

483
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:43,240
May your wish come true.

484
00:26:00,360 --> 00:26:01,440
Heizi. Heizi!

485
00:26:10,760 --> 00:26:12,360
This is too much.

486
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:13,200
We can't eat so much.

487
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:14,520
It's a waste.

488
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:15,760
I told her that,

489
00:26:16,080 --> 00:26:17,400
but I couldn't stop her.

490
00:26:18,800 --> 00:26:20,360
What are you doing, Fang?

491
00:26:20,800 --> 00:26:21,640
Showing off?

492
00:26:21,880 --> 00:26:22,800
You can take the leftovers back

493
00:26:22,800 --> 00:26:24,320
for Mr. Xiao and Yanqiu.

494
00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:25,840
We have been overworking recently,

495
00:26:25,840 --> 00:26:27,160
so we need to

496
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,080
eat something good.

497
00:26:28,600 --> 00:26:29,640
That's true.

498
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:32,480
Hongjun have lost
several kilograms of weight.

499
00:26:33,280 --> 00:26:34,320
Come on, Hongjun,

500
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:36,960
have some meat.

501
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:38,840
I'm alright.

502
00:26:39,840 --> 00:26:40,400
Here.

503
00:26:40,760 --> 00:26:41,480
Thank you, Chunsheng.

504
00:26:49,600 --> 00:26:51,720
Chunsheng is not recovered yet.
He needs nutrition.

505
00:26:52,120 --> 00:26:53,800
I... I'm fine.

506
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:54,880
I'm good.

507
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:57,960
Chunsheng,

508
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,680
I have to toast you.

509
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:02,160
If it hadn't been for you that day,

510
00:27:02,320 --> 00:27:03,160
- I would have...
- Hongjun, stop.

511
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:04,800
What are you doing?

512
00:27:05,120 --> 00:27:07,000
We have always been
looking after each other like this.

513
00:27:07,320 --> 00:27:08,160
No,

514
00:27:08,560 --> 00:27:10,160
it's different this time.

515
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:13,400
If I can't pass the exam,

516
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:14,200
we can forget it.

517
00:27:14,360 --> 00:27:15,480
But if I really pass it,

518
00:27:15,720 --> 00:27:17,680
I will owe you

519
00:27:18,320 --> 00:27:19,280
a big one.

520
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:21,440
So I have to thank you.

521
00:27:21,880 --> 00:27:23,040
Hongjun, cut it out.

522
00:27:23,240 --> 00:27:24,760
Don't worry about it.

523
00:27:25,120 --> 00:27:26,440
We are brothers.

524
00:27:27,280 --> 00:27:28,800
Come on, let's drink.

525
00:27:29,160 --> 00:27:29,960
- Cheers.
- Wait a minute.

526
00:27:30,560 --> 00:27:31,160
What?

527
00:27:31,240 --> 00:27:32,120
What's wrong with you?

528
00:27:32,280 --> 00:27:34,080
Hongjun did well in the exam.

529
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:35,400
He will definitely pass it.

530
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:38,360
Fang is always reliable.

531
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:40,200
I believe what she said.

532
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:43,640
I also think I'll make it.

533
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:46,480
I really want to enter Peking University.

534
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:48,120
I think their Chinese Language Department

535
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,800
is particularly good.

536
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:50,640
Good.

537
00:27:51,120 --> 00:27:52,160
What about you, Fang?

538
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:53,840
Fang wants to enter
the Foreign Language Department.

539
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:54,760
She is good at English.

540
00:27:56,080 --> 00:27:56,720
That's great!

541
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,120
Come on, let's have a toast.

542
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:00,960
That's why we need to thank you.

543
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:03,360
Stop saying that, come on.

544
00:28:14,320 --> 00:28:14,840
Fang,

545
00:28:15,480 --> 00:28:17,680
there's something I need to figure out.

546
00:28:18,520 --> 00:28:19,920
Are you thanking me

547
00:28:20,560 --> 00:28:22,120
for Hongjun

548
00:28:22,520 --> 00:28:23,880
or for yourself?

549
00:28:26,040 --> 00:28:26,760
For myself.

550
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:28,560
That means

551
00:28:28,680 --> 00:28:30,120
you think I'm a good person.

552
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:31,400
Certainly.

553
00:28:32,840 --> 00:28:34,000
So you mean

554
00:28:34,240 --> 00:28:36,040
it's good for Hongjun

555
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:37,440
to have a friend like me?

556
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:42,360
Did you hear that?

557
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:44,920
She has changed her opinion.

558
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:47,040
I remember that not long ago,

559
00:28:47,360 --> 00:28:48,520
if I'm not wrong,

560
00:28:49,240 --> 00:28:50,520
it was on Guohua's birthday.

561
00:28:51,360 --> 00:28:53,000
At that table. Hongjun, was it that table?

562
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:54,560
I remember it was that table.

563
00:28:54,560 --> 00:28:55,480
That's it, right?

564
00:28:55,800 --> 00:28:56,920
What did you say that day?

565
00:28:57,240 --> 00:28:58,440
Did you say that

566
00:28:58,560 --> 00:28:59,920
Hongjun did nothing

567
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:02,800
but fighting and chasing girls all day

568
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:04,440
when he was with me?

569
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:05,960
Don't push it.

570
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:08,240
Do you want me to help you remember

571
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:09,480
your glorious past?

