Instead,

595
00:30:00,560 --> 00:30:02,040
I think you made the right choice.

596
00:30:02,600 --> 00:30:04,240
There are always
some people in this world

597
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:05,280
who put others' interests first.

598
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:06,560
And I believe

599
00:30:06,800 --> 00:30:08,920
you will be a very good doctor

600
00:30:08,920 --> 00:30:10,720
in the future.

601
00:30:11,800 --> 00:30:13,240
You too can be

602
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:14,240
an excellent soldier.

603
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:16,600
Thank you.

604
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:24,320
How dare you!

605
00:30:24,320 --> 00:30:24,720
Beat him!

606
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:26,960
Who do you think you are?

607
00:30:27,800 --> 00:30:28,760
You one-eyed punk!

608
00:30:28,840 --> 00:30:30,840
Look at yourself!

609
00:30:30,880 --> 00:30:33,120
I have raised such a good girl,

610
00:30:33,360 --> 00:30:34,560
how can I let you get her?

611
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:35,240
Beat him!

612
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:36,520
Beat him hard!

613
00:30:37,360 --> 00:30:39,400
I told you to keep an eye on him,

614
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,720
but you ignored me!

615
00:30:40,760 --> 00:30:42,000
You are also responsible.

616
00:30:42,280 --> 00:30:43,760
Heizi, Heizi.

617
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,200
Do you want to marry me?

618
00:30:45,320 --> 00:30:45,960
Yes.

619
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:47,720
I can't hear you. Louder.

620
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:48,640
Yes!

621
00:30:49,320 --> 00:30:51,560
What did you say? Yes?

622
00:30:51,720 --> 00:30:52,560
Yes?

623
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:53,960
Then bear with it.

624
00:30:54,360 --> 00:30:55,280
Let me tell you.

625
00:30:55,280 --> 00:30:56,640
These are all family.

626
00:30:57,040 --> 00:30:59,120
Your future father-in-law
and brothers-in-law.

627
00:30:59,280 --> 00:31:01,160
It's not shameful to be beaten by them.

628
00:31:01,280 --> 00:31:03,360
Yes, I know.

629
00:31:04,120 --> 00:31:05,680
Dad, listen to me,

630
00:31:05,960 --> 00:31:08,280
