647
00:31:45,320 --> 00:31:46,440
or have a concussion or something.

648
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:48,240
I don't care

649
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:49,480
if you don't care.

650
00:31:49,920 --> 00:31:50,800
Xiaohui,

651
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:52,960
are you determined to marry him?

652
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:56,880
What's so good about him?

653
00:31:57,200 --> 00:31:58,520
