666
00:32:18,840 --> 00:32:20,520
I swear in front of everyone,

667
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:22,800
including Heizi,

668
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:26,440
that I, Zhao Xiaohui,

669
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:28,720
will never leave Heizi.

670
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:29,840
As long as he doesn't kick me out,

671
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:31,120
I'll be with him all my life.

672
00:32:31,480 --> 00:32:32,520
I, Zhao Xiaohui,

673
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:34,240
will keep your word.

674
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:38,720
Dad, look at her!

675
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:49,680
Heizi,

676
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:51,520
do you want to marry me?

677
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:55,240
