685
00:33:17,120 --> 00:33:17,720
No problem!

686
00:33:18,520 --> 00:33:19,200
I'll get it now!

687
00:33:19,560 --> 00:33:20,920
What are you doing?

688
00:33:24,800 --> 00:33:26,800
You want me to take him to the hospital?

689
00:33:27,640 --> 00:33:29,520
You beat him up,
who else should do that?

690
00:33:31,820 --> 00:33:35,460
(Long live our great Party
