733
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:59,200
practice boxing with Dong after work,

734
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:00,760
and read books at home at night.

735
00:36:02,400 --> 00:36:03,520
It's a pity that

736
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:06,160
the stack room of the
neighborhood committee was closed.

