00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:08,920
I have no access to a lot of books now.

738
00:36:12,160 --> 00:36:13,480
Your daily life is colorful.

739
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:15,120
It's an association of activity and inertia.

740
00:36:16,320 --> 00:36:18,200
It's not as colorful as yours for sure.

741
00:36:19,200 --> 00:36:19,960
Look at you.

742
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:21,840
You have been working hard
for your dream.

743
00:36:22,600 --> 00:36:24,000
You take college lectures,

744
00:36:24,320 --> 00:36:26,840
