801
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:35,520
The Military Region Newspaper is
the most important one in our military region.

802
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:36,840
Only the best commanders

803
00:38:37,040 --> 00:38:39,040
of each troop

804
00:38:39,040 --> 00:38:40,520
