with admiration.

807
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:45,680
Is that helpful enough to you?

808
00:38:46,200 --> 00:38:47,640
But why did you ask that?

809
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:49,400
Nothing.

810
00:38:49,400 --> 00:38:51,200
You said you were gonna be on it,

811
00:38:51,200 --> 00:38:52,040
so I'm happy for you.

812
00:38:53,720 --> 00:38:55,000
I don't think he's serious.

813
00:38:55,240 --> 00:38:57,320
And I don't even know
if I'm qualified or not.

814
00:38:59,040 --> 00:39:00,600
Alright, it's getting late.

815
00:39:00,640 --> 00:39:01,680
I'd better leave now.

816
00:39:02,200 --> 00:39:02,680
OK.

817
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:03,840
I'll be here

818
00:39:03,840 --> 00:39:05,040
for a few more days.

819
00:39:05,160 --> 00:39:06,040
I'll come to visit you when I'm free.

820
00:39:07,320 --> 00:39:08,520
Goodbye, Comrade He Hongling.

